Flash games
1.in github make a new repsository and name it whatever then go to a flash games website i will use papas pezzeria
2. go to inspect and go to the network tab (if it does not show go to the 2 >>) then in filter type swf then reload the page
3. then you should find an swf right click it and open in a new tab once its downloaded go to github and click on add file then put the swf
4.then go to settings and go to pages and and scroll down untill you see branch and switch none to main and then click save
5. click on the swf file in github click the copy icon by the name then go back to Settings>Pages click on the link by "your site is live at"
6. You Should get a page and it says 404 at the top click on the URL bar and at the end of the url paste the thing you copied then copy the URL
7.Get the code from the "Embed code Ruffle Flash" then go to google sites and make a new game page and go to insert tab
8. click on embed paste the code from "Embed code Ruffle Flash" then you should see a line that looks like this "player.load("your-file-name.swf");"
9. change inside the quotaion marks to the URL you copied then click next and insert it should load.
10. done!!!!!!!!!
